    • similar

      public boolean similar(AbstractItemStack<? extends org.spongepowered.api.item.inventory.ItemStack> compare)
      Returns true if the provided item is similar to this. An item is similar if the basic information is the same, except for the amount. What this includes: - material - display - modelData - flags - lore - attributes - enchantments

      What this does not include: - Item Data.

      Specified by:
      similar in interface AbstractItemStack<org.spongepowered.api.item.inventory.ItemStack>
      Parameters:
      compare - The stack to compare.
      Returns:
      True if the two are similar, otherwise false.
